    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯天然气过剩表明奥地利仍处于克里姆林宫的能源轨道上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/russian-gas-glut-shows-austria-still-in-kremlin-s-energy-orbit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利盛产俄罗斯天然气，这使得俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司的长期客户能够增加对其邻国的销售，同时推迟从克里姆林宫控制的能源转向的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/russian-gas-glut-shows-austria-still-in-kremlin-s-energy-orbit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的财富因救济集会而增加 56 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/gautam-adani-s-wealth-swells-by-5-6-billion-on-relief-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，印度最高法院结束了一场诉讼听证会后，高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 旗下公司的股价上涨，使他的净资产增加了 56 亿美元。市场监管机构正在调查针对该集团的广泛企业渎职指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/gautam-adani-s-wealth-swells-by-5-6-billion-on-relief-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 03:17:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在邦民意调查中大获全胜，推动印度市场反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-decisive-win-in-state-elections-boosts-india-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在三场关键州选举中取得胜利，巩固了该党在明年全国大选前的地位，推动印度股市基准创下新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-decisive-win-in-state-elections-boosts-india-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 03:09:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在邦民意调查中获胜有望提振印度资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-win-in-state-polls-seen-boosting-case-for-india-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场参与者表示，总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的政党在关键州选举中获胜可能会增强印度对外国投资者的吸引力，并吸引更多资金流入当地股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/modi-s-win-in-state-polls-seen-boosting-case-for-india-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 01:34:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
