    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对反弹的怀疑，对冲基金加大了看跌日元的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/hedge-funds-boost-bearish-bets-on-yen-to-most-in-19-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测日元近期反弹将是短暂的，对冲基金上周将日元看跌押注提高至 2022 年 4 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/hedge-funds-boost-bearish-bets-on-yen-to-most-in-19-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 00:53:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德 128 亿美元的 Origin 收购要约被投资者拒绝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/brookfield-set-for-12-8-billion-snub-as-origin-investors-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Origin Energy Ltd. 股东以微弱优势投票否决了 Brookfield Asset Management Ltd. 牵头的 191 亿澳元（128 亿美元）收购案，此前该基金对一家对澳大利亚能源转型至关重要的公用事业公司进行了一年的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/brookfield-set-for-12-8-billion-snub-as-origin-investors-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 23:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
